column5: Well about two months ago we switched to a Voice over IP phone. Biggest mistake of my life. I won't bother going into all the gory details but as of noon this Saturday we will be back to a land line but unfortunatly we will also have a new phone number so for those of you with the old one, please update your records.  Our new number will be 705-328-0577
Will test the new number Saturday afternoon to make arrangements for Sunday...
